    "Kennel_Card_Website_Memo": "Hi, I’m Rebel! I’m a young, energetic guy who loves to play, stay busy, and be part of the action. At about 50 pounds, I’m a great medium size — easy to handle, perfect for adventures, and just right for everyday life. I’ve also got the cutest little nub of a tail and a sweet face that’s guaranteed to melt your heart! I’m treat-motivated and eager to learn, which makes training fun and rewarding. I would thrive in an active home that enjoys walks, playtime, and continuing my training so I can be the best boy I can be. I love my toys and sometimes guard them because they’re very special to me. I’ll do best with a family who understands this behavior and is willing to help me work on sharing and trading games to build my confidence and good habits. If you’re looking for a fun, smart, and affectionate companion with a big personality in a perfectly sized package, I might be your guy!",
