    "Kennel_Card_Website_Memo": "Meet Bailee — a beautiful young mixed breed around a year and a half old with one striking blue eye and one warm brown eye that make her impossible to forget. Right now, the shelter has been a very overwhelming place for Bailee. The loud noises, constant activity, and unfamiliar environment can feel scary, and she would much rather find a quiet place to hide than rush up to meet new people. But underneath that nervous exterior is a sweet girl who is already making progress every single day. With patience, gentle voices, and a few tasty treats, Bailee has started learning that people can be kind and safe. Since arriving, she’s come a long way — happily taking treats and even leaning in for soft head scratches once she begins to trust you.",
